BEDROXX!!!

I'M SO EXCITED YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW!!!


<3333

i went shopping today with my mom. it was my shopping spree day! weeeee! it was oober fun! and also i got lots-o-stuff. it was exciting. my mom and i had lots of fun too! hehe. i got stuff from the "good stores. as in not from Hollister, American Eagle, etc. But i did get stuff from, Forever 21, Ross, Urban Mix, Levis, RAVE, and Victoria Secret. haha i so needed a good bra. the ones i had barely worked. and now i don't move when i walk! yay! tis exciting! well i guess you all didnt need to know that. especially if you're a guy. haha sorry...

so i got back from my california trip. we were supposed to go whale watching, to the Wild Animal Park, and to Magic Mountain but at the last minute my dad didnt really want to go to the animal park. and then we found out the six flags was closed to the public. which was totally LAME. i was excited for that too. wah! o well. i can wait til' next year when we go with church. that always so much fun! 

so i pretty much have no plans over break. except for a broadway show on sunday night. i was going to go to the switchfoot concert, but i wanted to hang out with friends more, especially since i just got back from my trip and all. so yeah... i pretty much wrote a lot.

ok bye bye and to anyone who read this... i love you! hehe


( oh yes and heather, we are having a sleepover with a tent and i will call you! cause i am excited like that)

love love love
i was depressed for a few days. i feel better.

Imuris ended like a week ago... it was AMAZING. i don't know what else to say. God has spoken to me in sooo many ways since it has ended.. its incredible! im soo happy to finally feel sooo close to God! I feel like this year at imuris i connected much more to God. 

not only did i get closer to God, but also with the whole high school group, especially the senior girls! i am so happy to feel so connected to the community. wow imuris has changed my life!

So Me Sarah, Kelsea and Andrea started a sisterhood. heck yes! ASKA is what it is called. we also have a myspace for it! alright! its pretty flippin sweet. we are sooo making beanies! haha! but yeah... soo thats my life in a nutshell. 

i thought i liked this guy, but i have no chance... THE END

So yeah im totally watching a really old movie. The Parent Trap, with Lindsey Lohan. Yeah when she was like 10, or whatever. Its wierd because she was so cute, and now shes, like, i dunno not so cute. 

well yeah after that i think sarah and i are ging to watch A Goofy Movie. Kinda excited for that one.

Thought i would inform you.

Wow! I haven't updated in forever! I'm kinda mad because myspace it totally not working right now! arg... 

Today was really boring. It was a tuesday conference so i had like these really boring classes for an hour and a half EACH!

-Drivers Ed 
-English
-Geometry

So pretty much boring. Even though after Drivers Ed i was walking to lunch and this guy, who is pretty cute talked to me. But i think he was just being friendly. o well it was still kinda cool.

Soccer is over. I don't even think i mentioned that it started. But yeah. 

And i accidently ate raw beef today. That was grotesque(sp?)
MERRY CHRISTMAS FOOLS!

Wow i just saw Pride and Prejiduce! It is probably the best movie made! (well too girls that is) I highly suggest you all go see it! It was so romantic, and amazing! Its my new favorite movie!

haha just thought i woul like to tell you...

Mucho Amor!
HAPPY THANKSGIVING!

wow i havent been on in a while... well i have been on but i havent updated. my dad rode in the Tour De Tucson. he got a flat tire, but he still finished his race. ummm this weekend is so relaxing! im really tired and need the physical and mental rest. especially from soccer. we had to run a lot in soccer on friday. we ran just about  4 miles yesturday. you guys should be proud of me. i didnt walk at all!!! yay!!! well i dont like anyone right now, just so you guys know. gabe and i decided we should just be friends. i dont reall know what it means to like someone. so if you people could tell me in a comment it would be very useful!!! thanks!!!

see you on the flip side (whatever that means)
Ok, Refuge Refuel was AMAZING!!! I will go into the details when i get more rest and can type properly. Yes, that sentence took me a long time to type, so goodbye!

CDO WON!!! I'm kinda sad in the fac5t that my school lost, but im kinda happy we did because we were way to cocky before the game! And CDO deserved it. They played hard and earned the win. Well just about everyone was there! There was Me, Sarah, Emily, Heather, Andrea, Aaron, Ben, Paul, Austin, Josh, Garret, Gabe, Phil, and of course Jeremy!!! And I convinced Max to come to this game and he did! i was so happy i havent seen him in like, a half a year! I think Gabe might be mad at me for inviting him. maybe. Well it was really fun!!! And crowded!!!

I made the soccer team! yay! JV. but JV is much more fun than V. And the coach seems much nicer. Emily made it too, along with a lot of our old players on JV last year. which is good because we already know how to play togther as a team! I'm so stoked for the season! Well g2g watch The sisterhood of the Traveling Pants!!!

mucho amor

wow, so tired!!! im sore and i have a headache... and im gong to bed.. now! soccer was sooo hard today. we had to run 2 1/2 miles and then do sprints then do soccer then do jogging (my favorite part) im so sore im going to do sooo badly tomorrow. and my lower back is so sore from diving as goalie that first day. ahhh, please please pray for me to get... unsore (haha) i need to do good to make the team. i think i might do diving team next year, instead of soccer. well good night!!!

As you all know today was halloween. for most people it is a joyful holiday where you go out and get tons of candy are rot your teeth out. but for me it was lame. i went to school, found out i got a C on my spanish test, went to soccer try-outs and was bored out of my mind cause the coach sucks, and went home and stayed home. i was sitting on my couch watching Moulin Rouge (if thats how you spell it) answering the door and giving out candy to the little kids, and stuffing my face with some as well. and thats what i did, all night, and i swore i missed a few trick or treaters cause i wasn't paying attention, but o well at least they are still little kids and get to go trick or treating. they should be happy they at least have that. 

so basically my life s dull, but magic mountain is coming in 10 days and im super excited!!!! can't wait, going to pop a blood vessel in brain and die from anticipation.

That play was good!!! But the story is tired in my mind, so next one i see is The Lion King!!! woot woot!!! 

I am dreading school tomorrow, and it worries me...

today i had to miss church to go to this pumpkin carving thing that this man my dad works with invited him to. it was fun when we were carving the pumpkins. but after that it was pretty much boring. emily jon and i were dancing the robot to the techno songs that came on. then we all crammed into the small little playhouse and sat in littl plastic chairs for a while. then we all saw a spider and freaked and ran out of there. it was funny because it looked weird that all these high school/middle school kids running and screaming bloody murder out of a little playhouse. haha. we have to go to see Annie on Broadway tonight. fun, but i would rather see a movie with my friends. but o well... :(

i just got back from the homecoming game! fun fun fun!!! except for the fact that it was flippin freezing!!! weird how its cold out but its in arizona. i know crazy. we won, of course, cause thats how we roll. well when i was at the game i ate cotton candy with sarah and andrea, sat with the band again (woot), saw tons of people, congradulated mitchell on winning homecoming lord (psh whatever i voted for truitt), stuck a glowstick in my hair, and danced a little. fun night. 

i wont be coming to church on sunday :( totally bummed major. my parents have this pumpkin carving thing we all hve to go to. i dont know why but whatever, so im missing out on Jakc's sermon!!! arg!!! but i think i will get over it eventually after a few years of mourning. well im like really pooped so i think im gonna stay on for a little and then go to bed, so farewell to all thee reading this. i don't know if that made sense but i'm trying to practice my shakespeare because we are reading Julius Ceasar in english so... ya

tata

i just got back from the U of A football game.we went for andrea's surprise sweet 16 party! We lost. but its all good it was super fun.i think i lost my voice though. haha. i saw a lot of people i knew there. like 12! after that we all went to peter pipers pizza and played games, haha, and ate pizza of course!!! then mellisa drove us home. wow good day. i have a lot more to tell but i am really tired and have a major head ache so... goodnight.

well today was just great! It rained after school when i was walking home so that was nice. then i ran throught he sprinklers in front of my neighborhood. it was super fun! i had tons and loads of geometry hw, all proofs, and a lot of Spanish too! But i got it all done! i made a gourmet salad for diner that i'm sure everyone will enjoy!

oooo more pluses! gabe can go to magic mountain! yay! and bob is really fun to talk to, i dont know why but, he is. i don't think gabe likes me talking to him but, i like to so, poo on you gabe!!! haha 

sad thing is jeremy is not sure if he can go! that stinks! i want everyone to be there and heather can't go either which already ruins half of the enjoyment! ahhh but i will try and call her like every chance that i get! and tell her what happens!!! weeeeee ok as you can tell im very happy right now!! haha

ok bye!

i feel a little better than i did yesterday. today i took the PSAT's and it is a load off of my stress. but still dont feel like myself. i want to mope around a lot. but i am going out to coffee with my small group and hopefully i get to hang out with the boys after that. i hope! I havent hung out with them all break, so... yeah. 

Amanda

bad day... 

i need something abrupt and happy to happen... and i dont even know if that could help. when i got home i took my dogs for a walk. it was cool and smelledlike rain. normally that would make me feel much better... but as i was walking i was getting more and more upset at myself. so i decided to run. i took off my flip flops and ran as fast as i could home with the dogs. i flopped on my bed and went to sleep. 

i still dont feel good...

and i dont know who to turn to most of the people i would turn to wouldn't get it.

im getting my ears peirced today!!!!!!!!!!!! yay!!!!!!!! im a little nervous and a little excited!!!! but i think the excitement outweights the nervousness. haha emilt and her little friends plan to have a get together/ sleep over or something and i kinda wanted them to have it at our house so me and sarah can hang out with them and they can see my ears... haha sounds weird. but i thin kthey want to do it at heathers i guess.

tata

Well today was sunday as most of you all know. well yesturday was sunday.. it is kinda late.. or early. haha. we went to church as usuall. sarah and i worked with the little kids. they are soooo adorable. i cant wait til im a mommy! well i can wait. hehe anyway. after church we hung out and i took a nap for an hour of two. then we went to our leadership meeting which was really good by the way. I went home and now andrea is here. no we did not see the corpse bride cause heather needs to see it with me!!! im soo excited. we watched smallville and a little of the first old superman movie. lol good stuff! then we watched grease cause andrea has never seen it!!! i know right!!! its crazy!!! so ya now im here... doing this.

Yesturday i went to meredith's b-day party which was oober fun! we went to pizza and then a movie. the greatest ame ever played. it was very surprisingly good!!! dont you ever talk to my cady again! hehe love that!!! we went back to meredith's and made t-shirts, watched mulan and slept!!!! it was a blast!!!

well lots-o-love

amanda

Football game tonight!!! im totally going!!! its @ 7:00 and its @ IRHS!!! im wearing my I ♥ drumline t-shirt i made! too bad jerms isnt gonna be there. poop. he went to colorado right after school. dang it!

conditioning was gay. josh was really mean today... evil. we were doing 20 push ups and he was counting mine. it was gay cause i cant do them... like... at all. my elbows crack and pop whenever i go down so it kinda hurts... lol. and i told him and he was all... do 20. ahhh evil

wow havent like updated in like forever. well... today i went to my sister's cross country meet. emily and sarah did really well. i was kinda bummed that i missed out on a movie that i wanted to see really realy bad with my friends and now i have to totally go alone. it sucks cause i thought they didnt even want to see that movie but... they did, with out me. i think im gonna cry... wahhh. o well i wasnt home...

i had lots-o-fun yesturday! we went to church which is always fun for me!!! then ater church we met Austin, jeremy, heather, gabe, james, josh, and cory at wendy's for lunch. heather and i got salads and nuggets. we crumpled them on topof our salads! heck yes! haha. anyway. after that we walked to the mall and bought heather shoes. haha poor heather. then we went to barnes and noble and hung out in there for a while. paul was gonna jump but a man saved him. haha. then we all wenbt to my house to watch hide and seek. that was super fun! after everyone left i had andrea over and heather wagli emily andrea and i played cranium!!! and we also watched interview with the vampire. lol andrea was disturbed! lol. well it was a super fun day and i loved it. 

then today i had the first soccer conditioning since like last season! it was super hard. tons of sprints!!!! i hated it but im going back tomorrow i think. hehe i have to do the responcible thing! lol. kinda fun as in the whole begining when we stretched. haha

 

lot-o-love 

panda bear

sarah and i went to a mountain view footbal game last night. game was boring and we didnt know anyone except for Josh and Gabe who met us there. o yeah... we knew Tim too. I went to sarah and emily's cross country meet up in chandler and it was fun i guess. except for the hot, bug biting part. cheering strangers on in the races was fun cause you could boost their self confidence. well tonight there is a cross country party at wades house and i guess i have to be there. even though i dont really feel like i belong. and tomorrow i think we are all going to heather's house. i give you the details later!

bye bye

Manderzzz

today was kinda boring... im so glad we have wnac tomorrow!!! i really need it!!!

and i really need the sweedish fish sarah is bringing!!! yay!!!

Amanda

We went to jerms house today. me sarah jerms (duh), josh, gabe, and cory were there. first we all sat around and watched cellular for a while. then we went quading. it was amazingly fun. i didnt drive though i was too scared that i would kill myself. anyway. then we went swimming. and after that we sat around and drank caprisun and listened to musci. then sarah and i left cause she had X-country. its ruining my life and im not even doing it. haha!

confused...

arguments are never fun especially with phil and gabe. :(

that movie was ok everyone else hated it but i think it was alright. i did not have that much fun at all. maybe i shouldn't go to movies anymore. this was definitly the worst time i have had in a while. 

i quit...

:(

Im gonna go to the mvies with my friends and we are seeing The Transporter 2... even though i haven't seen the first one... haha. Well i hope i have fun cause i haven't had that much fun in a while. i'm gonna call Andrea and ask her to come becuase i Heart her!

Tell you about it when i get back!!! 

Love...


Amanda Panda Bear♥

Got back from the football game a while ago. we won! yay! It was like 50-7 haha. Flowing Wells... I saw Shannon in the band at the game. yay! jeremy and phillip did awesome in the half time show! way to go guys! im totally making a shirt for you! seriously! Gilbert came at the end of the game but i didn't see gabe... hmmm that shows how much he cares! haha just kidding gabe! anywho well im reallt tired and i feel like crap so.. 

bye bye!

Today is the first IRHS football game of this year! I'm soo excited! I hope we win! That would be super!
 

My brother and my dad are going to a MLF game in phoenix today. Cardinals vs. Broncos. They got free tickets from some guy at my dad's work. Well nothing else to say... 
 

Byes

I saw Red Eye last night!!! It was very good and definitly kept your attention. I went with, Heather, Soni, Emily, Sarah and Ryan. It was super fun. After the movie we sat in the food court for a while. i got a yummy cinnamon sugar pretzel!!! it was soooo good!!! After that we went to Old Nazy and messed around a bit. Heather tried on this shirt and it looked good but she didn't have any money so... well we all didn't have that much money either. Haha!!!

Well i'm outty!!!! 

Love to all, i'm gonna go eat some food!!!

Amanda Panda Bear

Well school was fun today!!! I got to all of my classes fine and i knew at least a few people in each of them. My english 10 teacher is really cool! But my Honors Geometry teacher is dislexic??? How ever you spell it. But how the heck is he supposed to write on the board if hes dislexic??? Anyway... Sam is in my Spanish 2 class and thats cool cause she was in my Spanish 1 class last year. We are learning Spanish together!!! Hmmm... I have Aerobics with Emily and Hannah so that should be fun!!!

I saw Yarrel at lunch today... I turned around and walked away. I guess i'm too much of a pansy to walk by him with all that happened and all. It was good to see Ryan today. he was being very friendly and I think he would definitly mak ea good friend. Hmm... Haven't seen Brandon around. Kinda miss him throwing staples at me though... haha that was sarcastic!!! For those of you that didn't know.

The bus was late today. we were all standing there in the hot heat for like a half an hour!!! It was horrible!!! Ryan and Tracy drove by and were laughing at me!!! It was funny. The not so funny part was sweating to death in the heat! gosh it was horrible!!!

Well thats enough of my first day!!! It was actually my first first day of High School. I was sick last year on the first day!!! I know IRONIC much!!!

 

See you all tomorrow!!!

School Starts Tomorrow!!!

And i'm sooo not ready...

i went to the mall with my mom and sarah today. it was really fun. we went to The Island, which was a really really good movie. it definitly kept you on the edge of your seat! i liked the part when they were trying to kiss each other but had no idea how to do it. but its not like i know how either. hehe... embarassment. anywho... before that we went to applebee's!!! woot! i love that resturaunt (cant spell). we also went shopping for my little brother. got him some snazzy shirts and stuff. it was fun. well i enjoyed spending time with my mom. i wish i could have gotten together with my friends yesturday but i couldn't talk....

o well. i really miss them all and i havent seen them in like 3 weeks. well i'll see them on sunday or sooner i hope.

love love love love love x 1,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000 million!!!

Panda Bear

Well yesturday was really fun in an awkward, near death way. Haha. My grandpa let me and Sarah drive the golf cart around to get a feel for the wheel. haha that rhymes. anyway, ya i backed out of the garage garage pretty good then i over corrected and crashed into the bushes next to me so hard that Sarah almost flew out of the car. hehe. well the rest of the way i did fine. When it was Sarah's time to go she was all no i dont want to. well w/e. so ya that was basically my day. 

Today we hung out at the house. Then we went to see Batman Begins, again for us but my grandparents wanted to go so yay! I dont mind watching a movie i have seen already when Christian Bale is in it. haha. just kidding hes not that cute. hes ok. so after that Sarah and i went with my dad in the golf cart and Sarah drove! wow! CONGRADS SARAH! and then i drove again. The battery was low so my dad had to get out and push up the hills sometimes. but like only twice. Well today was fun. im gonna go eat some homemade cookies now. hehe. i'll talk to ya'll later. 

and we pick up Katie tomorrow! yay! i cant wait to see her. o ya we are taking pictures for you guys! dont worry! i love you all!

♥

Amanda Panda Bear

Well today was my first day of vacation. everyone was stressed when we were packin the car. (and by everyone i mean my dad) haha. well i love him. anyway. the drive to the airport was really short, probaly the only short drive i will have in the next two weeks.

We waited at the airport for an hour at the gate. while we were there we met this young man. probaly just out of college. He was stationed here in tucson and was flying back to Rhode Island to go to his family's funeral. He told us that they were all killed in a car accident. All of them. hi mom, dad, and younger brother. so my parents talk to him while i sat there listening to music (secretly eavesdropping) it was hard to hear though so there's nothing else to say.

Well the plane ride was long and boring. it was 3 1/2 hours long i think. or 4 hrs long. i dont know. but whichever it was, it was long.

We flew into Chicago and there we had 45 min to wait at our other gate to fly to Raliegh. or however you spell it. so we boarded that plane and that flight was much shorter. i slept the whole time. i dont ever know why but i did. haha. when that flight was over it was like... 8:00 in North Carolina. well im wide awake.

When we went to go rent a car we had some trouble. which is gay. the people were saying we couldn't get the car we had rented and we had to get another. but it wouldnt fit our luggage. so then they said that if we wanted a bigger one we had to pay $15 per day extra. so my dad started threatening to sue and stuff so we got the car. haha. but for $10 extra per day. which is still gay.

In the car ride to my grandparents house (one hour long) emily and jon were really wild. it started to get annoying. so i listened to music the whole time and stared out the window. it started to get dark and i only saw one star. :'( tear tear. kinda depressing.

Well now im at my grandparents house and im writing this entry for all of you guys back home. i really really miss you! and i will try and call you once i can find somewhere with a signal. which i cant right now so be patient. i miss you all and i love you!

Please please comment because this might be the only way i can talk to you and myspace. please pray for the man we met on the plane, and for phillip's leg! haha.

I love you all a million sweedish fish!

Amanda Panda Bear

Wow, where to start...

I am going to miss all of you sooooo much. I dont know why but whenever I am going on a trip I get all excited in the begining but as the trip gets closer the more and more I don't want to leave. Plus just when the weather starts getting good (rainy) i have to leave Arizona. Its kinda sad.

I'm also going to be missing the last two summer small groups. I really was starting to enjoy those too. :( Well its not like i knew what i was gonna be for holiday night and sports night. And Sarah S. was my small group leader and that was pretty cool cause considering I LOVE her and all!

I just for some reason am not feeling the trip right now. I really don't want to leave my friends. even though Heather is leaving pretty soon... Hopefully if her back gets better! I'm sorry hon! But I am just going to miss them all so much!

Well I'm definitly going to take tons of pictures and im keeping a journal so Heather can read it when i get back! Or when she gets back... w/e. Well I love you all so much and this might be my last journal entry in two whole weeks. unless I find a random computer somewhere. O well.

PROMISE TO BE HERE WHEN I GET BACK!!!

Amanda Panda Bear

Fun before we leave for our trip! I love you guys and i will miss you all! See ou in two weeks! Heather in like a month! I'll try and take pictures for you all! I love you all one million sweedish fish! PS: Heather i dont remember if i told you about that one guy that lived in maryland. you know that Max kid. well hes gonna be at the beach for a day. so pray for him to keep his distance. if you know what i mean. ;)
